"""
        Test that a TypeError is raised when an invalid value is used to set
        the object type of an ObjectDefaults structure.
        """
kwargs = {'object_type': 0}
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Object type must be an ObjectType enumeration.', objects.
    ObjectDefaults, **kwargs)
args = objects.ObjectDefaults(), 'object_type', 0
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'Object type must be an ObjectType enumeration.', setattr, *args)
